# Code Style Rules

## Python Style
```rules
python:
  formatting:
    line_length: 100
    quotes: single
    indentation: 4 spaces
    trailing_comma: true
    
  docstrings:
    style: Google
    required: [summary, args, returns, raises]
    max_length: 80
    
  imports:
    groups: [stdlib, third_party, local]
    sort: true
    max_line: 1
```

## Naming Conventions
```rules
naming:
  classes: PascalCase
  functions: snake_case
  variables: snake_case
  constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
  private: _prefix
  protected: _prefix
  
  patterns:
    plugins: "*Plugin"
    agents: "*Agent"
    tests: "test_*"
``` 